  "name": "RPlog_A_Gentleman_s_Disagreement",
  "title": "A Gentleman's Disagreement",
  "summary": "At the Cat's Claw cantina on Ord Mantell, New Republic Intelligence agent Drax Rendolen waits out the tedium of the field over a bottle of Corellian whiskey. He is joined by Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard, fresh from a fraught conversation with her daughter, and by the smuggler Jaspar Andromidas, who brings Ambrosia a custom doll covertly modified into a hidden flask. The mood sours when Drax's NRI handler Ivar arrives with armed agents, insisting Drax come in over irregularities in a medical scan and a bounty on his head that the brass fears compromises his operation. Refusing to be detained, Drax stuns the room into compliance, takes Ambrosia as a reluctant human shield, and backs out the rear exit before sprinting off down the alley as Ivar's agents give chase. Ambrosia is hauled back inside, shaken and indignant; an agent warns her to report any contact from Rendolen, but she quietly resolves to do as she sees fit, and she and Jaspar part with a promise to meet again under better circumstances.",
